cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Natural Language Processing (cs.CL) sub-categories, as it deals with video captioning and language entailment generation. It also involves machine learning techniques, which could place it in the Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, since it evaluates its approach on standard video captioning datasets, it could also be classified under Multimedia (cs.MM).
